      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MISS LADY BUG (6) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by 3 lengths at this track in a handy 22.38 beating Argyle Emma. Looks to have an edge on most of these. STAR OF VENUS (7) has missed the frame at his last two but did run well three back when third (23.20) in a Grade 5 at Geelong. Rates a winning chance on best. MISS COCO (1) pinged the lids and was in the firing line early but drifted out of it when 6th at Horsham in Grade 5 company. Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Should be about the money. ANGRY FRANKY (3) cannot be underestimated.",
